George Hackathorne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Hackathorne 0 George Hackathorne (February 13, 1896 – June 25, 1940) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 59 films between 1916 and 1939. His interment was located in Hollywood Forever Cemetery.
